   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y18.13 Var. a (mss. 6, 40, 88):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em>. čahār guftan pad buland wāng zōt ud rāspīg bē ham guftan frāgām abrāstan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "The <em>zōt</em> and the <em>rāspīg</em> should recite together four <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em>. with loud voice and raise the <em>frāgām</em>."</ab>
         <ab>Y18.13 Var. b (mss. 5, 6, 400, 410 (sec. m. marg.) ):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em>. čahār abāg rāspīg az pāy wāng buland guftan</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "(The <em>zōt</em>) should recite four <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em> together with the <em>rāspīg</em>, standing and with loud voice."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
